Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不确定  闭着眼睛就是了\N{\fnArial\fs32}It should be any minute, just keep your eyes closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,酷\N{\fnArial\fs32}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,仪式并未完成\N{\fnArial\fs32}The transfer is incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都是闭着眼睛的吗\N{\fnArial\fs32}Did everyone keep their eyes shut?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直闭着\N{\fnArial\fs32}I kept mine shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\fnArial\fs32}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦\N{\fnArial\fs32}Alright, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能偷看了那么一下下  可能\N{\fnArial\fs32}There's a chance I might've maybe probably looked. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞格比\N{\fnArial\fs32}RIGBY!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你做了什么吗\N{\fnArial\fs32}Do you have any idea what you've done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音\N{\fnArial\fs32}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,从外头传来的\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's coming from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,玛格丽特\N{\fnArial\fs32}Margaret?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是玛格丽特  当瑞格比偷看时...\N{\fnArial\fs32}That's not Margaret. When Rigby looked--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了可能  可能\N{\fnArial\fs32}I SAID MAYBE LOOKED, MAYBE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他释放出了玛格丽特秘密的守护者\N{\fnArial\fs32}He released the Guardian of Margaret's Secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她会因为我们偷看了秘密而毁灭我们\N{\fnArial\fs32}She will destroy us for looking at her secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办\N{\fnArial\fs32}What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个挽救的方法\N{\fnArial\fs32}There's only one way to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每个人吐露一个自己的秘密\N{\fnArial\fs32}Each of us must reveal a secret of our own,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不然她就会灭了我们\N{\fnArial\fs32}or she'll destroy us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我先来\N{\fnArial\fs32}Alright. I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以跳代走的原因\N{\fnArial\fs32}The reason I always skip is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了我这辈子  心里唯一思念过的女人\N{\fnArial\fs32}in all my life, my heart yearned for only one woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在一起时总是蹦蹦跳跳的\N{\fnArial\fs32}And we used to skip together all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,直到有天我失去了她\N{\fnArial\fs32}On the day I lost her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓余生的每一天都要蹦蹦跳跳的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I vowed to skip every day for the rest of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我才不会忘记我们在一起时的美好时光\N{\fnArial\fs32}so that I'd never forget the time we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,起..起作用了  现在快说出你们的秘密\N{\fnArial\fs32}I-IT'S WORKIN'! NOW TELL YOUR SECRETS!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我们要清理排水沟时\N{\fnArial\fs32}sometimes when we're supposed to be cleaning out gutters,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们其实是去喝咖啡了\N{\fnArial\fs32}we go to get coffee instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对  对  这个不错\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah, yeah, good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而且其中有很多次  我甚至都没点咖啡\N{\fnArial\fs32}And a lot of times, I don't even get coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不喜欢清理排水沟\N{\fnArial\fs32}I just don't feel like cleaning out the gutters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  必须是有意义的秘密\N{\fnArial\fs32}No, it has to be something meaningful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要有多大意义才行啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}HOW MEANINGFUL DOES IT HAVE TO BE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们不告诉她一个真正的秘密  我们就死定了\N{\fnArial\fs32}IF YOU DON'T TELL A REAL SECRET, WE'RE ALL GONNA DIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了  我来\N{\fnArial\fs32}ALL RIGHT, I'LL DO IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢跟着唱一些超烂的口水歌\N{\fnArial\fs32}I LIKE TO SING ALONG TO REALLY BAD POP MUSIC!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃过从垃圾桶里翻出来的甜甜圈\N{\fnArial\fs32}I ATE A DOUGHNUT OUTTA THE TRASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢不穿内裤\N{\fnArial\fs32}I LIKE GOING COMMANDO!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,经常不穿\N{\fnArial\fs32}A LOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实觉得从垃圾桶里翻出来的甜甜圈更好吃\N{\fnArial\fs32}I ACUALLY LIKE THE TASTE OF DOUGHNUTS BETTER WHEN THEY'RE FROM THE TRASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞格比  还记得我们预订了床垫\N{\fnArial\fs32}RIGBY! REMEMBER WHEN WE ORDERED BEDS FOR OUR ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的那块却一直没送来吗  其实我撒了谎\N{\fnArial\fs32}AND YOUR'S NEVER SHOWED UP?! I LIED!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我把两块床垫叠在一起了 我一直枕着它们\N{\fnArial\fs32}I STACKED THEM UP AND I'VE BEEN SLEEPING ON THEM THE WHOLE TIME!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  因为那实在是太舒服了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'M SORRY, DUDE, IT'S JUST TOO COMFORTABLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说真的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞格比  继续说\N{\fnArial\fs32}RIGBY! SAY SOMETHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候偷了邻居的自行车  还把它扔在了屋顶上\N{\fnArial\fs32}WHEN I WAS LITTLE, I STOLE MY NEIGHBOR'S BIKE AND THREW IT ON THE ROOF!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要更有意义的秘密\N{\fnArial\fs32}IT HAS TO BE SOMETHING DEEP!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我会藏起帕布的鞋子\N{\fnArial\fs32}SOMETIMES I HIDE POPS' SHOES
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我觉得他找鞋的样子很搞笑\N{\fnArial\fs32}CAUSE I THINK IT'S FUNNY WHEN HE'S LOOKING FOR THEM!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个讨厌的家伙\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'M A HORRIBLE PERSON!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌洗澡  讨厌猫咪\N{\fnArial\fs32}I HATE TAKING SHOWERS AND I HATE KITTENS!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实没参加过足球队\N{\fnArial\fs32}I LIED ABOUT BEING ON THE FOOTBALL TEAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得艾琳不戴眼镜的时候很迷人\N{\fnArial\fs32}I THINK EILEEN IS HOT WITHOUT HER GLASSES ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们完成仪式\N{\fnArial\fs32}Let's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来和玛格丽特那本一模一样\N{\fnArial\fs32}It looks exactly like Margaret's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,跳跳  我们该怎么报答你\N{\fnArial\fs32}Skips, how can we repay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得我说为什么我要以跳代走吗\N{\fnArial\fs32}You remember that stuff I said about why I skip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 记得啊  - 不  当你们没听过\N{\fnArial\fs32}- Yeah. - No, ya don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你睡了我的床垫\N{\fnArial\fs32}I knew it was my matress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳  是吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}So, Eileen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fnArial\fs32}STOP TALKING!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信  我们修复了日记\N{\fnArial\fs32}I can't believe we got the diary back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  累惨了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah, what a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不要帮玛格丽特浇花了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I never wanna water Margaret's plants ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  我们到底帮她浇了花没\N{\fnArial\fs32}Wait, did we actually ever water her plants?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她来了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  玛格丽特  旅行顺利吗\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, hey Margaret! How was your trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错  但我也只能忍受我爸妈这么久了 \N{\fnArial\fs32}It was nice, but i can only take my parents for so long, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快跟我说说  父母都很可怕\N{\fnArial\fs32}Tell me about it, 'rents are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用担心你的盆栽\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well, you don't have to worry about your plants,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你公寓的屋顶也还在  还有...\N{\fnArial\fs32}or if the roof is still on your apartment, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思就是一切都好\N{\fnArial\fs32}Because it's fine is what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没去帮我浇花吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}You guys didn't go and water them, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,去了呀  怎么\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘记其实我已经拜托过艾琳了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I forgot that I already asked Eileen to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fnArial\fs32}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  她整个周末都待在卧室里呢\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah, she had the spare bedroom all weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉给你们添了这么多麻烦\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry you guys went through all that trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没见着她  我想是正好错过了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I guess we just missed each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以别放在心上\N{\fnArial\fs32}So don't worry about it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对 没关系的\N{\fnArial\fs32} Yeah, it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,两位  这是你们点的咖啡\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hey, guys, here's your coffee.

